title: FULL SHOW: We Talk With Diddy, Recap 2022 BET Hip Hop Awards, Ask Yee and More
itunes:title: FULL SHOW: We Talk With Diddy, Recap 2022 BET Hip Hop Awards, Ask Yee and More
description:
Today on the show we have DIDDY! Yes the man himself! We talk a whole lot from new music, to legacy, to Caresha please! Later on we recap the 2022 BET Hip Hop Awards during the rumor report. And finally Angela gives listeners business and relationship advice during "Ask Yee"
